criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

        - 200 consecutive adult patients scheduled for elective surgery requiring endotracheal
        intubation

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  BMI > 35 kg.m-2);

          -  chronic obstructive pulmonary disease;

          -  history of difficult intubation;

          -  mouth opening < 3 cm;

          -  inadequate neck mobility;

          -  history of oropharyngeal pathology.
